        "card_heading": "About Kinetic Motorcycles",
        "card_content": "<p>Kinetic Motorcycles was founded in 2013 by Mike Le with a focus on original design, functional innovation, and in-house manufacturing. From the beginning, the goal has been to create well-engineered motorcycle parts that combine performance, usability, and distinctive design.</p><p>We specialize in products designed by Mike and manufactured in the United States, allowing for consistent quality control and close attention to detail. Our work is rooted in the hand-built motorcycle community, where fitment, function, and individuality matter. We focus on original designs built to support customization, reliability, and long-term use.</p><p>Our goal is simple: <strong>provide the right parts, at the right standard, backed by real support.</strong></p>",
